Package prkmodel.types

Interface NeuronGuestElement

All Superinterfaces:
NervousSystemElement
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractNeuronGuestElement, RepastNeuronGuestElement
public interface NeuronGuestElement extends NervousSystemElement
Interface representing a guest element attached to a neuron in the nervous system. It extends the NervousSystemElement interface to include properties and behaviors specific to guest elements.
